{
  "video_id": "uoujHpVJSe8",
  "title": "Talking to machines - 6 Minute English",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 7880.0,
      "end_time": 10219.0,
      "text": "Rob: Hello and welcome to 6 Minute"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10220.0,
      "end_time": 11260.0,
      "text": "English. I'm Rob."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11260.0,
      "end_time": 12719.0,
      "text": "Dan: And I'm Dan."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 12720.0,
      "end_time": 14740.0,
      "text": "Rob: Hey Dan. What’s the time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14740.0,
      "end_time": 17240.0,
      "text": "Dan: Time you got a new watch?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17240.0,
      "end_time": 19392.0,
      "text": "Rob: Now I didn’t ask you that just for a"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19393.0,
      "end_time": 21460.0,
      "text": "joke or a sarcastic comment now did I?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21460.0,
      "end_time": 23840.0,
      "text": "Dan: Well no, but look there’s a clock over"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23840.0,
      "end_time": 25780.0,
      "text": "there, and you are wearing a watch, you"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25780.0,
      "end_time": 28180.0,
      "text": "have a smartphone and a computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 28180.0,
      "end_time": 29840.0,
      "text": "all of which show the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29840.0,
      "end_time": 31810.0,
      "text": "So why are you asking me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31810.0,
      "end_time": 34339.0,
      "text": "Rob: Dan! I was trying to introduce today’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34340.0,
      "end_time": 37440.0,
      "text": "topic which is all about virtual assistants"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 37440.0,
      "end_time": 38460.0,
      "text": "or bots."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38460.0,
      "end_time": 40500.0,
      "text": "You seemed to have forgotten the script."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40500.0,
      "end_time": 43320.0,
      "text": "Dan: Oh yes, sorry. We’re talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 43320.0,
      "end_time": 46000.0,
      "text": "software that you talk to and that can talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 46000.0,
      "end_time": 48840.0,
      "text": "back to you. Like Apple’s Siri, Google’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 48840.0,
      "end_time": 51340.0,
      "text": "Assistant, Amazon’s Alexa and"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51340.0,
      "end_time": 53340.0,
      "text": "Microsoft’s Cortana."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 53340.0,
      "end_time": 56200.0,
      "text": "It might be on your phone or computer or"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 56200.0,
      "end_time": 58440.0,
      "text": "even a speaker in your house."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 58440.0,
      "end_time": 60814.0,
      "text": "Rob: Now before we hear more about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 60814.0,
      "end_time": 63259.0,
      "text": "topic, here is today’s quiz question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66340.0,
      "text": "Do you know when was the first computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 66340.0,
      "end_time": 68900.0,
      "text": "which could recognise speech, launched?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68900.0,
      "end_time": 75140.0,
      "text": "Was it in a) 1951 b) 1961, or c) 1971."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 75140.0,
      "end_time": 78220.0,
      "text": "Dan: I have found my script, so I’ve seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 78220.0,
      "end_time": 80940.0,
      "text": "the answer but I have to say I was"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80940.0,
      "end_time": 81880.0,
      "text": "surprised."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 81940.0,
      "end_time": 83399.0,
      "text": "Rob: Don't tell anybody Dan, OK. We’ll give"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83400.0,
      "end_time": 85780.0,
      "text": "the answer for the listeners at the end of"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 85780.0,
      "end_time": 88380.0,
      "text": "the programme. We’re going to hear now"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 88380.0,
      "end_time": 90500.0,
      "text": "from Tom Hewitson, who is a"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 90500.0,
      "end_time": 92900.0,
      "text": "conversation designer, working in the field"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92900.0,
      "end_time": 96560.0,
      "text": "of virtual assistants, talking on BBC Radio"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 96560.0,
      "end_time": 98560.0,
      "text": "4's Word of Mouth programme."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 98560.0,
      "end_time": 101340.0,
      "text": "He talks about the whole idea of virtual"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 101340.0,
      "end_time": 103800.0,
      "text": "assistants and how they are changing the"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 103800.0,
      "end_time": 106196.0,
      "text": "way we interact with technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106200.0,
      "end_time": 108180.0,
      "text": "How does he describe our existing"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 108180.0,
      "end_time": 110660.0,
      "text": "relationship with computers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 110660.0,
      "end_time": 112820.0,
      "text": "Tom Hewitson: It changes the way that"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 112832.0,
      "end_time": 114818.0,
      "text": "we think about computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 114819.0,
      "end_time": 116855.0,
      "text": "To date we’ve thought of them largely as"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116855.0,
      "end_time": 118840.0,
      "text": "tools. They’re just an advanced version"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 118840.0,
      "end_time": 121381.0,
      "text": "of a calculator. They’re something you"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 121381.0,
      "end_time": 123941.0,
      "text": "kind of use to get a specific thing done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 123941.0,
      "end_time": 126209.0,
      "text": "whereas this is kind of changing them"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 126209.0,
      "end_time": 128600.0,
      "text": "more into like an agent. They’re an active"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 128600.0,
      "end_time": 131340.0,
      "text": "participant in the kind of interaction and in"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 131340.0,
      "end_time": 134000.0,
      "text": "guiding you to make the right decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134000.0,
      "end_time": 135956.0,
      "text": "Rob: How did he describe our existing"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 135956.0,
      "end_time": 137589.0,
      "text": "relationship with computers then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 137590.0,
      "end_time": 139426.0,
      "text": "Dan: He said that to date, which is an"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139426.0,
      "end_time": 141192.0,
      "text": "expression which means 'up until this"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 141193.0,
      "end_time": 143850.0,
      "text": "point in time', we have thought of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 143850.0,
      "end_time": 144640.0,
      "text": "as advanced calculators."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 144640.0,
      "end_time": 146859.0,
      "text": "Rob: Yes, that’s right, we use them as a"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 146860.0,
      "end_time": 149700.0,
      "text": "tool to get things done. But he says that"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 149700.0,
      "end_time": 151980.0,
      "text": "modern technology is turning them into"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 151980.0,
      "end_time": 153329.0,
      "text": "an agent."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 153330.0,
      "end_time": 154860.0,
      "text": "This doesn’t mean a secret agent, like"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 154860.0,
      "end_time": 157980.0,
      "text": "James Bond! In this sense an agent is"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 157980.0,
      "end_time": 160359.0,
      "text": "something that has agency and that"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 160360.0,
      "end_time": 162860.0,
      "text": "means it has the ability to act individually"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 162860.0,
      "end_time": 164920.0,
      "text": "and make its own decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 164920.0,
      "end_time": 166739.0,
      "text": "Dan: I’m not sure I’d like my phone to have"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 166750.0,
      "end_time": 169149.0,
      "text": "agency. It probably wouldn’t like being"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 169149.0,
      "end_time": 170440.0,
      "text": "in my pocket all day."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 170440.0,
      "end_time": 172600.0,
      "text": "Rob: Who would Dan? But I’m not sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 172600.0,
      "end_time": 174960.0,
      "text": "Hewitson is suggesting our devices would"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 174960.0,
      "end_time": 177580.0,
      "text": "become that clever but he did say they"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 177580.0,
      "end_time": 180280.0,
      "text": "could become more active in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 180290.0,
      "end_time": 183331.0,
      "text": "Dan: Maybe. I imagine, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 183340.0,
      "end_time": 185420.0,
      "text": "telling us if we are spending too much"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 185420.0,
      "end_time": 187200.0,
      "text": "time in fast food restaurants?"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 187209.0,
      "end_time": 189359.0,
      "text": "Rob: Maybe in your case Dan. Mine would"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 189359.0,
      "end_time": 192351.0,
      "text": "be telling me I spend too much time in the gym!"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 192351.0,
      "end_time": 194972.0,
      "text": "Hewitson goes on to explain how"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 194972.0,
      "end_time": 197600.0,
      "text": "the way we will talk to our virtual"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 197600.0,
      "end_time": 198424.0,
      "text": "assistants will develop."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 198424.0,
      "end_time": 201340.0,
      "text": "What does he say we don’t need to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 201340.0,
      "end_time": 202840.0,
      "text": "Tom Hewitson: We will develop our own"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 202840.0,
      "end_time": 204900.0,
      "text": "kind of vernacular for speaking with"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 204900.0,
      "end_time": 206100.0,
      "text": "machines that will be subtly"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 206100.0,
      "end_time": 207960.0,
      "text": "different from how we speak to other"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 207960.0,
      "end_time": 210180.0,
      "text": "people because as you rightly point out"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 210180.0,
      "end_time": 211760.0,
      "text": "you don’t need to make the machine like"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 211760.0,
      "end_time": 214660.0,
      "text": "you don’t need to kind of make random"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 214660.0,
      "end_time": 217253.0,
      "text": "chit-chat that’s just filling the time. It can"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 217253.0,
      "end_time": 219429.0,
      "text": "be much more brusque and to the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 219430.0,
      "end_time": 221607.0,
      "text": "Dan: A lot of what we say in human"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 221607.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "communication is to do with our"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225590.0,
      "text": "relationship with the person we’re talking to."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 225590.0,
      "end_time": 227960.0,
      "text": "Rob: We say things and talk about things"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 227960.0,
      "end_time": 229760.0,
      "text": "that are maybe not directly relevant to our"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 229760.0,
      "end_time": 233440.0,
      "text": "point. With a digital virtual assistant, we"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 233440.0,
      "end_time": 235780.0,
      "text": "don’t need to do that, so we don’t need to"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 235780.0,
      "end_time": 237379.0,
      "text": "make the machine like us."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 237380.0,
      "end_time": 239519.0,
      "text": "Dan: Hewitson said that we will develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 239520.0,
      "end_time": 242000.0,
      "text": "our own vernacular, this is a general word"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 242000.0,
      "end_time": 244900.0,
      "text": "for a native language. This vernacular will"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 244900.0,
      "end_time": 247600.0,
      "text": "be a little bit different from our everyday"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 247600.0,
      "end_time": 250100.0,
      "text": "vernacular because, as we said, we don’t"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 250100.0,
      "end_time": 252180.0,
      "text": "need to maintain a social relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 252180.0,
      "end_time": 254200.0,
      "text": "with the artificial assistant."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 254200.0,
      "end_time": 255380.0,
      "text": "Rob: This means that we won’t need"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 255380.0,
      "end_time": 258190.0,
      "text": "chit-chat. Chit-chat is another expression"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 258190.0,
      "end_time": 260700.0,
      "text": "for small talk: conversation topics which"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 260700.0,
      "end_time": 263418.0,
      "text": "aren’t important but are part of everyday"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 263418.0,
      "end_time": 265773.0,
      "text": "social communication, like talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 265773.0,
      "end_time": 266480.0,
      "text": "the weather."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 266480.0,
      "end_time": 268000.0,
      "text": "Dan: And because we don’t need to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 268000.0,
      "end_time": 270180.0,
      "text": "friends with our virtual assistants, we can"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 270180.0,
      "end_time": 272900.0,
      "text": "be brusque and to the point. Both of these"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 272900.0,
      "end_time": 275159.0,
      "text": "mean being very direct and not very"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 275160.0,
      "end_time": 276210.0,
      "text": "polite."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 276210.0,
      "end_time": 278219.0,
      "text": "Rob: Well Dan, I don’t mean to be brusque but"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 278220.0,
      "end_time": 280456.0,
      "text": "it is time for the answer to this week’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 280460.0,
      "end_time": 282919.0,
      "text": "quiz question. Earlier I asked when was"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 282920.0,
      "end_time": 284500.0,
      "text": "the first computer which could recognise"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 284500.0,
      "end_time": 287600.0,
      "text": "speech, launched. The options were:"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 287600.0,
      "end_time": 292320.0,
      "text": "a) 1951, b) 1961, or c) 1971."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 292320.0,
      "end_time": 294380.0,
      "text": "Well actually the first computer which"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 294380.0,
      "end_time": 298800.0,
      "text": "could recognise speech was launched in 1961."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 298800.0,
      "end_time": 301990.0,
      "text": "Dan: Yep! It was called the IBM Shoebox and"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 301100.0,
      "end_time": 303680.0,
      "text": "could recognise 16 words and the"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 303680.0,
      "end_time": 306558.0,
      "text": "numbers zero to nine. That’s nearly as"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 306558.0,
      "end_time": 307840.0,
      "text": "many as you!"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 307840.0,
      "end_time": 310270.0,
      "text": "Rob: Cheeky! Right enough of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 310271.0,
      "end_time": 312919.0,
      "text": "chat-chat. Let’s recap today’s vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 312919.0,
      "end_time": 315207.0,
      "text": "Dan: Well chit-chat was one of today’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 315207.0,
      "end_time": 317480.0,
      "text": "expressions. Meaning 'small talk', but we"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 317480.0,
      "end_time": 320259.0,
      "text": "also had the expression to date. That"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 320259.0,
      "end_time": 322550.0,
